data.description: This charming property offers a spacious and comfortable living experience with its 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, and a generous 3,148 square feet of living space. Located in the desirable Pine Tree ISD.  Built in 1980, this well-maintained residence showcases timeless appeal and thoughtful design. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an inviting atmosphere that exudes warmth and comfort. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal space for entertaining guests or spending quality time with loved ones. The kitchen boasts ample counter space, modern appliances, and plenty of storage options, making it a chef's dream. The bedrooms are generously sized, providing a peaceful retreat for everyone in the household. The master suite features a private en-suite bathroom, offering a serene oasis to unwind after a long day. Don't miss out on the chance to make this house your home. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and potential of 1201 Ridgeview Ln.
